title: Ep. 688 - The Real Identity - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Ganpati puja has started in the Gokuldham society. The kids are also educated on various Ganpati stories by Gajanand. Daya also asks him to have food with them and tells it's her courtesy to take care of the guests.

title: Ep. 689 - A Stain On Bhdie's Clothes - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Madhavi, by mistake, spills 'kumkum' on Bhide's clothes. The residents make fun of him. Later, the kids want to organize a fancy dress competition and Bhide agrees to arrange it in the clubhouse.

title: Ep. 690 - Fancy Dress Competition - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: As decided, a fancy dress competition is organized. All the residents present their unique style of dressing. Popatlal gets emotional seeing Komal dressed up like a newspaper.

title: Ep. 691 - Entertainment Galore - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: The residents put up a show filled fun and laughter. Dressed up as uniquely as possible, they entertain the audience.

title: Ep. 692 - Unique Dressing Styles - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: The fancy dress goes with the others dressed up uniquely representing various things. We see Daya acting as a school going kid, Jetha dressed up as a jalebi and Baga as traffic police.

title: Ep. 693 - Gokuldham's Rabrindranath Tagore - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Taarak dressed up as Rabindranath Tagore while the kids represent various armed forces of the courses. Meanwhile, Roshan's fancy dress impresses everybody.

title: Ep. 694 - Gajanand's Surprise - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: The fancy dress competition comes to an end. Gajanand has promised a surprise for the residents and presents them with the same. Bhide asks everybody to be prepared for the Ganesh idol immerssion tomorrow.

title: Ep. 695 - Where Is The Money? - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: The immerssion processs starts. The residents go in search of the box of money but see its missing. They doubt Gajanand. They go to the hospital and find his family. He also confesses his crime.

title: Ep. 696 - Taarak Is Fed Up With Anjali - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Taarak is fed up with Anjali upon eating the same old food every day and complains that he can take it no more. Meanwhile, Daya tells Jetha that he's got a new name! Watch to fid out what it is.

title: Ep. 697 - Baagha Surprises Jetha - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Nattu Kaaka and Bagha go to Jetha with a deal in hand. Jetha is surprised to hear that Bagha owns a bigger showroom than Jetha and asks him why is he working as a repairer in his small showroom and asks him to leave.

title: Ep. 698 - Daya's News Upsets Jetha - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Jetha is super hungry and is waiting for dinner, only to hear that Bapu ji has asked everyone to eat only 1 meal a day. Upon seeing, Jetha is intolerant to this decision, she relieves him by that she was just joking.

title: Ep. 699 - Will Jetha Find A Way Out? - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Jetha is in a fix, as Taarak has approached him to be his new fire brigade. He's come to have lunch over at his house as he's fed up with eating salads all the time. Meanwhile, Anjali has promised Daya that she wouldn't feed him.

title: Ep. 700 - All's Well That Ends Well - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: This proverb turned out to be true for Dr. Haathi as in the end the food Daya had prepared for Jetha alone, was consumed by Dr. Haathi, leaving both Jetha and Taarak upset.

title: Ep. 701 - A Troublesome Day At The Bhide's - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Bhide ends up destroying the Jetha's cheque and goes to Jetha's house to get himself another one, only to find out that they're leaving for Pune, and that Tapu will be staying with him for the rest of the day.

title: Ep. 702 - A Trip To Pune - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Jetha, Daya and Baapu Ji go to Pune to pay a visit to Ram Ji Kaaka, who had met with an accident. But something enigmatic happens as it leaves them astonished. Watch to find out what could it be?
